=<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            border-left: 5px solid #2196F3;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #d32f2f;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #2196F3;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>SSL Certificate Expiry Notice</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="message">
            <p>Dear Team,</p>
            <p>The SSL certificate for the website <strong>{{ $json.result.host }}</strong> is set to expire in <span class="highlight">{{ $json.result.days_left }}</span> days.</p>
            <p>Please take the necessary actions to renew the certificate and ensure uninterrupted service.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>The IT Operations Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
